snippet: CHELOUCHE--Roslyn R. (Ros), May 24, 1937-December 31, 2015. Loving mother of Adina Chelouche (George Tellides); cherished grandmother of Alexander, Theodore and Julia Tellides. Services will be held at Plaza Jewish Community Chapel, NYC on January 7 at 12:45pm. 1/3
